Pretty much any time Fox News talks about climate change temperatures?<p><a href="http://www.politifact.com/punditfact/statements/2015/feb/13/dana-perino/fox-news-host-climate-scientists-fabricated-temper/" rel="nofollow">http://www.politifact.com/punditfact/statements/2015/feb/13/...</a><p><pre><code>  &quot;They&#x27;re (the White House) actually kind of lucky that we don&#x27;t cover climate change as much as we should,&quot; Perino said.

  &quot;Because yesterday, it was reported that the temperature readings have been fabricated and it&#x27;s all blowing up in their faces.&quot;

  Co-host Kimberly Guilfoyle interjected that it was &quot;fraud science&quot; and Perino said, &quot;Yes, I agree.&quot;
</code></pre>
